      "rationale": "In-vitro experiments were conducted at flow rates of 2–6 L/min and rotational speeds of 2000–3500 RPM matching CFD boundary conditions. Temperature, fluid viscosity, and inlet pressure were controlled and documented within ±3% of target values."
